            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Espalier 1.0.2</h2>
                <ul>
                  <li><b>Expand any card</b> — click a card's body to open it full-size, with a quick color picker.</li>
                  <li><b>Columns and stacks</b> — reorder cards in a column, fan out a stack, and move a whole column to another board.</li>
                  <li><b>Much faster on big boards</b> — scrolling large boards is now smooth.</li>
                  <li><b>Templates and a welcome board</b> — every template opens with example cards, plus a guided welcome board.</li>
                  <li><b>Choose your editor font</b> — in Settings, under Editor.</li>
